posts.title: Miss that girl with large breast - missed connections
posts.body: I sure miss a girl with large breast. Is that you and your single give me a jingle

posts.title: you carried your own grocery containers. - missed connections
posts.body: We've chatted before. Haven't seen you in over a year.You used to carry a big Tupperware type container in your grocery cart, so you wouldn't have to use bags.You had brown hair and were thin.
